quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  21,30,"Ese abahakanye ntibabonye ko ibirere n’isi byari bifatanye nyuma tukabitandukanya, kandi ko buri kinyabuzima cyose twakiremye mu mazi? Ese ubwo ntibemera"
  21,31,"Nuko dushyira imisozi ishimangiye ku isi kugira ngo itabanyeganyeza, ndetse tunayishyiramo inzira kugira ngo bamenye aho banyura"
  21,32,"N’ikirere twakigize igisenge kirinzwe, nyamara birengagiza ibitangaza byacyo (izuba, ukwezi, inyenyeri)"
  21,33,"Ni na We waremye ijoro, amanywa, izuba ndetse n’ukwezi; buri cyose kigenda mu nzira zacyo cyihuta"
  21,34,"Kandi nta n’umwe mu babayeho mbere yawe (Muhamadi) twahaye kubaho ubudapfa. Ese niba wowe uzapfa, ni bo bazabaho ubuziraherezo"
  21,35,"Buri wese azasogongera ku rupfu, kandi tuzabagerageresha ibibi n’ibyiza. Ndetse iwacu ni ho muzagarurwa"
  21,36,"N’iyo abahakanye bakubonye (yewe Muhamadi), nta kindi bagukorera uretse kukunnyega (babwirana bati) “Ese uyu ni we uvuga (nabi) imana zanyu?” Nyamara iyo havuzwe (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe, barahakana"
  21,37,"Umuntu yaremanywe kamere yo kugira ubwira. (Vuba aha) nzabereka ibimenyetso byanjye (ibihano), bityo mwinsaba kubyihutisha"
  21,38,(Abahakanyi) baravuga bati “Ese isezerano (ryo guhanwa) rizasohora ryari niba koko muri abanyakuri?”
  21,39,"Iyo abahakanyi baza kumenya (uko bazaba bameze), igihe bazaba badashobora gukumira umuriro kugera mu buranga bwabo cyangwa mu migongo yabo, cyangwa ngo bamenye ko batazatabarwa (ntibari kuguma mu buhakanyi)"
  21,40,"Ahubwo (imperuka) izabageraho ibatunguye, ibateshe umutwe, kandi ntibazashobora kuyikumira ndetse nta n’ubwo bazarindirizwa (kugira ngo bicuze)"
  21,41,"(Niba bakerensa ubutumwa bwawe, yewe Muhamadi, ntukagire agahinda) kuko mu by’ukuri n’intumwa zabayeho mbere yawe zarakerenshejwe, maze abazisekaga bagerwaho n’ibihano by’ibyo basuzuguraga"